<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-row>
      <v-col
        sm="4"
        class="pa-3"
        v-for="product in products"
        :key="product._id"
      >
    <v-card></v-card></v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
import API from "../api";
export default {
  name: "Home",
  data() {
    return {
      products: [],
    };
  },
  async create() {
    this.products = await API.getAllProduct();
  },
};
</script>
